// Copy to `.env.test` (gitignored) to record real recipe API traffic locally
// via `npm run test:record`, without pasting a key on the shell each time —
// see vitest.config.ts and test/helpers/vcr.ts. Not needed for ordinary
// `npm test`: playback uses a placeholder key (the VCR excludes it from the
// cassette).

// ARC_API_KEY: same key as `.dev.vars` (ARC-AGI-3 web console). Backs the
// arc-game recipe's recorded.spec.ts.
ARC_API_KEY=
